<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨٤٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3919">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ مَسْلَمَةَ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«الْخَيْلُ فِي نَوَاصِيهَا الْخَيْرُ إِلَى يَوْمِ الْقِيَامَةِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>